# MOBILE::SCRIPT_IS_MOVING_MOBILE_PHONE_OFFSCREEN

## Parameters
* **BOOL** value

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
If bool Toggle = true so the mobile is hide to screen.
If bool Toggle = false so the mobile is show to screen.
